{"tid":304540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當李嘉誠上習總握手長達10秒，揭李生見證香港改變","createTime":"2017-07-01T03:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T04:07:20.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d74bf94ca7aeb98952e9e44dc6f3d298032cbb16","tid":304540,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:38:22.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平繼續第二天訪港行程，下午將在會展會見本港政商界人士，今晚出席特區政府設的歡迎晚宴及文藝晚會。習近平接見政商界人士時，與長實主席李嘉誠握手長達13秒，期間曾交談，待遇明顯與其他嘉賓有別。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/113803_bd7fe13f7a5a3e3e2a4431542b8d508f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F113803_bd7fe13f7a5a3e3e2a4431542b8d508f.jpg&h=2e106b21&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/113804_4f22eb44b8458d814b5eb1938ef26eb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F113804_4f22eb44b8458d814b5eb1938ef26eb2.jpg&h=4ce1af11&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/113805_d20729ad7029031471be39caff36da2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F113805_d20729ad7029031471be39caff36da2e.jpg&h=4396349c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/113809_d87c90e125ea9fc454f202a4881e28f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F113809_d87c90e125ea9fc454f202a4881e28f1.jpg&h=b224b10e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/01/113810_8f7f4c29af657718887fa812e1bf8fbf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F01%2F113810_8f7f4c29af657718887fa812e1bf8fbf.jpg&h=bf626acd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"edec9e2d7e2ba13a2dba0721e2c40883dce3ea25","tid":304540,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited